ProcurementCardUser_Note_Translation is a Form
    Layout
        paragraph
            Base_BusinessClass.ProcurementCardUser
                display as text
        single column
            IsoLocale
                compact format
                raise yellow alert when (VerifyTranslations_Note)
                    mouse over text is untranslatable:"The base data has been changed but this translation has not been verified"
        single column
            blank line
            Base_BusinessClass.Note
                label is untranslatable:"Note"
            Note
                label is untranslatable:"Translated"
